#~ msgid ""
#~ "Kai Krellis was only a child, so he needed help to rule intelligently. "
#~ "Mermen rule without official advisors, but Krellis relied on the wisdom "
#~ "of a priestess named Cylanna. She had been a friend of his father, and he "
#~ "had known her as long as he could remember."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kai Krellis era solo un bambino, così aveva bisogno di aiuto per regnare "
